mutil.title: Portable Suicen AX - W026S In-ear Wireless Headset Headphone Earphone with FM Radio Noise Suppression for Computer NoteBook HDTV DVD MP3
mutil.desc:
Features:
The item includes a Transmitter, a Receiver and a wired earphone. 
With this product, you can watch the HDTV at home and not disturb your other family members.
Connect the Transmitter with the audio source (such as, TV / PC / CD / DVD) via the audio connecting cable.
Supports FM Radio and Noise suppression.
The included 3.5mm audio jack can be used to the wired earphone. 
The transmitting distance is more than 30m.
With compact portable design, easy to carry.
Applications: Outdoor sports, morning exercise, etc. 

Installation: 
1.Correctly install 2 pieces of AAA (Not Include) batteries into the battery slot of the Receiver. 
2. Correctly install 2 pieces of AAA (Not Include) batteries into the battery slot of the Transmitter.
Operations:
1. Connect the Transmitter with the audio source (such as, TV / PC / CD / DVD) via the audio connecting cable.
2. Move the Power Switch of the transmitter to “ON” position, the indicator lamp shows red light. 
3. Turn on the Power Switch of the Receiver, and the indicator lamp will be bright.
4. Press the “Reset Button”, then press the “Scan Button”, the first channel is the audio signal of the Transmitter, and then adjust the volume to moderate level, you can enjoy the wonderful music. 
FM Radio:
1.The Receiver can be used as a separate FM Radio.
2.Turn on the Power Button / Volume Button of the Receiver, the indicator light will be bright.
3.Press the “Reset Button”, then press the “Scan Button”. The Radio will automatically scan your favorite broadcast programmers, and it can receive the FM frequency: 88 ~ 108MHZ.  
4.The item uses the PLL system, the signal is stable.

P2P cloud service, including cloud connecting, cloud monitoring, cloud transmitting to access IPC and NVR at any time and any place. It supports all channel image display on one screen at same time, support 4 channels’ image display by mainstream, and 4 channels playback.

Features:
Embedded Linux operating system.
P2P cloud service, including cloud connecting, cloud monitoring, cloud transmitting to access IPC and NVR at any time and any place.
Support Onvif protocol, support High profile S, High profile G, compatible with different IP camera that based on Onvif, RTSP standard.

The recording files in the USB disk can play directly in the playback interface while the snapshot pictures can be viewed directly.

Support 64G TF card(Not included).
Support alarm recording and picture memory and motion detection.
